{"word":"ζεῦξις","slug":"ζεῦξις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ζεῦξις</b></el> <el>(ζεῦξις, εως) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ζεύγνυμι'><el>ζεύγνυμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a yoking</i> or <i>manner of yoking</i> oxen, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a joining</i>, as by a bridge, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}